  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving] Unsuspend 1 of your Digimon, and for
    each Tamer you have in play, return 1 Option card with [Plug-In] in its name
    from your trash to your hand.[Your Turn] When you use an Option card with a cost
    of 2 or more, 1 of your opponent''s Digimon gets -3000 DP for the turn.'
